        <li class="pb-4">Teacher in the Graduate Program in Textile Design at SENAI/CETIQT-RJ, <span style="white-space: nowrap">2012–2013</span>.</li>
        <li class="pb-4">Teacher at EARJ American School of Rio de Janeiro <span style="white-space: nowrap">2012–2014</span>.</li>
        <li>Over 700 video lessons on Photoshop, Illustrator, and InDesign, created for Metapix courses. (<a href="https://www.youtube.com/@metapixvideos" target="_blank" class="text-link">available on YouTube</a>)</li>
